{{Campaignbox 罗马-波斯战争}}
公元224年，[[阿尔达希尔一世|阿尔达希尔一世]]击败帕提亚帝国，并以[[萨珊王朝|萨珊帝国]]取而代之。他在[[泰西封|泰西封]]掌握权力之后，几乎随即就开始侵袭罗马领土。230年代早期，[[亚历山大·塞维鲁|亚历山大·塞维鲁]]对萨珊波斯发动了一场大规模入侵，被波斯军队逐出并蒙受重大伤亡<ref>[https://books.google.fr/books?id=g4ZmqsyC5kEC&pg=PA158&lpg=PA158&dq=siege+of+nisibis+252+sassanian+victory&source=bl&ots=DWaraUPxK8&sig=hucBK8p05iTBSaHTwn1tsUggO6A&hl=fr&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=true/ A Companion to the Roman Empire] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.fr/books?id=g4ZmqsyC5kEC&pg=PA158&lpg=PA158&dq=siege+of+nisibis+252+sassanian+victory&source=bl&ots=DWaraUPxK8&sig=hucBK8p05iTBSaHTwn1tsUggO6A&hl=fr&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=true/ |date=20200725080458 }} "Ardashir began to raid the Roman territory almost immediately after he had taken power at Ctesiphon, making Roman armies look plodding and inept. When Alexander launched a massive invasion of his territory in the early 230s, Ardashir drove it back, inflicting heavy casualties.</ref>。[[努賽賓|尼西比斯]]在235或237年被波斯军队围攻，并最终被占领。

